\c 1
\s Kwaziso
\p
\v 1 Petro, muapositori waJesu Kristu, kuvaeni vakasanangurwa vekupararira kwePonto, Garatia, Kapadhokiasi, Asia, neBhitiniasi,
\v 2 maererano nekuziva zviri mberi kwaMwari Baba, mukuita vatsvene kweMweya, pakuteerera nekusasa kweropa raJesu Kristu: Nyasha nerugare ngazviwanzwe kwamuri.
\s Nhaka yakachengeterwa vakasanangurwa
\p
\v 3 Wakaropafadzwa Mwari naBaba vaIshe wedu Jesu Kristu, iye zvichienderana nekuwanda kwetsitsi dzake wakatiberekazve patariro inorarama kubudikidza nekumuka kwaJesu Kristu kubva kuvakafa,
\v 4 panhaka isingaori neisina kusvibiswa uye isingabvuruvari, yakachengeterwa imwi kumatenga,
\v 5 \add imwi\add* munochengetwa nesimba raMwari kubudikidza nerutendo kuruponeso rwakagadzirirwa kuzarurwa panguva yekupedzisira.
\v 6 Yamunofara mairi zvikuru, \add kunyange\add* ikozvino kwechinguvana, kana zvichifanira, muri pakushungurudzwa mumiedzo yakasiyana-siyana,
\v 7 kuti kuedzwa kwerutendo rwenyu kunokosha zvikuru kupfuura kwegoridhe rinoparara, kunyange ichiidzwa nemoto, kuwanikwe mukurumbidzwa nerukudzo nekubwinya pakuonekwa kwaJesu Kristu;
\v 8 iye musina kumuona munomuda; iye ikozvino musinga\add mu\add*oni asi munotenda kwaari, munofara nemufaro usingatauriki uye unorumbidzwa,
\v 9 muchigamuchira mugumo werutendo rwenyu, ruponeso rwemweya \add yenyu.\add*
\v 10 Nezveruponeso urwu vaporofita vakabvunzisisa nekunzvera, ivo vakaporofita zvenyasha dzinouya kwamuri;
\v 11 vachinzvera kuti panguva ipi kana yakadini Mweya waKristu aiva ari mavari yaakaratidza, paakagara apupura matambudziko maererano naKristu, nekubwinya shure kweizvi.
\v 12 Kwavari kwakaratidzwa kuti kwete kwavari ivo, asi kwatiri vaishandira zvinhu izvi, zvamunoparidzirwa ikozvino nevakakuparidzirai evhangeri neMweya Mutsvene wakatumwa kubva kudenga, zvinhu izvo vatumwa zvavanoshuva kunyatsoongorora.
\s Ivai vatsvene
\p
\v 13 Naizvozvo masunga zviuno zvemurangariro wenyu, zvidzorei, mutaririre zvakakwana kunyasha dzinouyiswa kwamuri pakuratidzwa kwaJesu Kristu;
\v 14 sevana vanoteerera, musingazvifananidzi nekuchiva kwakare pakusaziva kwenyu.
\v 15 Asi sezvo wakakudanai ari mutsvene, nemwiwo ivai vatsvene pamafambiro ose;
\v 16 nokuti kwakanyorwa, \add kuchinzi\add*: Ivai vatsvene, nokuti ini ndiri mutsvene.
\v 17 Zvino kana muchi\add mu\add*idza Baba, iye pasina rusarura anotonga zvinoenderana nebasa reumwe neumwe, garai panguva yeutorwa hwenyu mukutya;
\v 18 muchiziva kuti hamuna kudzikunurwa nezvinoora, sirivha kana goridhe, pamafambiro enyu asina maturo a\add ma\add*kagamuchira kumadzibaba enyu;
\v 19 asi neropa rinokosha raKristu seregwayana risina charinopomerwa uye risina gwapa.
\v 20 Iye zvirokwazvo wakagara azikanwa nyika isati yavambwa, asi wakaratidzwa panguva dzekupedzisira nekuda kwenyu,
\v 21 iye wamunotenda naye kuna Mwari, wakamumutsa kubva kuvakafa, akamupa kubwinya; kuti rutendo rwenyu netariro zvive kuna Mwari.
\p
\v 22 Manatsa mweya yenyu pakuteerera chokwadi kubudikidza neMweya mukuda hama nekusanyengera, dananai zvikuru nemoyo wakachena;
\v 23 maberekwa kutsva kwete zvichibva pambeu inoora, asi isingaori, neshoko raMwari rinorarama nekugara nekusingaperi.
\v 24 Nokuti nyama yose yakaita seuswa, nekubwinya kwose kwemunhu seruva reuswa. Uswa hwunosvava, neruva rahwo rinodonha;
\v 25 asi shoko raIshe rinogara nekusingaperi. Uye iri ishoko rakaparidzirwa kwamuri neevhangeri.